ill deliverable** end-to-end.\n- We had hiccups (like fetch/gateway instability), but they **didn’t stop completion** because we had working paths/fallbacks.\n\nIf you want, I’ll split future reports into:\n1) **Delivery blockers (hard stop)**\n2) **Operational issues (annoying but survivable)**\n3) **Risks (could become blockers)**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba4943d59c819bb3fd7aa2bb977325\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":3067,"output":234,"cacheRead":13312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16613,"cost":{"input":0.00536725,"output":0.003276,"cacheRead":0.0023296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01097285}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773816128503}}
