evant chunks from both BM25 + vector\n- rank evidence\n- return answer like:\n  - “Yes, Nava recommends …”\n  - Sources: `navahc.com/...` + quoted lines/chunks\n\n---\n\nSo what you *see* as user is:\n- a clean answer,\n- confidence/evidence context,\n- and clickable source provenance.  \n\nIf you want, I can run one real query now and paste the exact output format we currently have.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba49f70cd0819ba346945a09bfbbb6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":370,"output":273,"cacheRead":16512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17155,"cost":{"input":0.0006475,"output":0.003822,"cacheRead":0.0028896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0073590999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773816305592}}
