 top (angle taxonomy, channel formatting rules, novelty scoring, cadence).\n\nSo verdict:  \n- **RAG = strong foundation (truth + retrieval)** ✅  \n- **Need one more layer for content performance/systematic posting** 🔧\n\nIf you want, I’ll build that next layer now: a **Nava Idea Engine** that outputs channel-ready idea batches (LinkedIn/X/FB + You/Yosef voice variants) from RAG results.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba4a7d5fd4819b9b7ca85b8533acd2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":218,"output":273,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17643,"cost":{"input":0.0003815,"output":0.003822,"cacheRead":0.0030015999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007205099999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773816438147}}
