0_bbb6jhDHDZn04On6ZjsoWuV\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Creating prioritized skill setup checklist**\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Yes. Here’s the **today execution list** to end with a queued batch of posts.\n\n## Today’s Objective\nBy EOD: **produce a ready-to-queue content batch** (LinkedIn + X mandatory, FB optional-by-fit, Tiny + Yosef variants where useful).\n\n## Priority Plan (in order)\n\n1) **Skill/tool research + setup (first task)**\n- Audit missing capabilities for Nava workflow.\n- Install/config only high-confidence safe tools.\n- Define what each tool is for (ideation, drafting, image refinement, scheduling, docs critique).\n- **Deliverable:** `SKILLS_SETUP_TODAY.md` with selected stack + setup status.\n\n2) **Lock content engine spec (v1)**\n- Finalize taxonomy, output schema, and guardrails (domain/evidence enforced).\n- Define channel/persona transforms (Tiny, Yosef, Nava).\n- **Deliverable:** `CONTENT_ENGINE_SPEC_V1.md`.\n\n3) **Update pipeline for “new article ingestion”**\n- Add/update process so each new Nava article is fetched, chunked, indexed quickly.\n- **Deliverable:** `INGEST_UPDATE_RUNBOOK.md` + working script/command sequence.\n\n4) **Create idea bank from current corpus**\n- Generate 25–40 vetted ideas from RAG.\n- Filter to strongest 12–20 for this week.\n- **Deliverable:** `IDEA_BANK_YYYY-MM-DD.md` (with sources per idea).\n\n5) **Draft queue-ready posts**\n- Build batch:\n  - LinkedIn: 6–10 posts\n  - X: 6–10 posts (1–3 tweet structures)\n  - FB: 2–4 only if high fit\n- Include Tiny/Yosef variants where needed.\n- **Deliverable:** `QUEUE_BATCH_V1.md` + per-post source mapping.\n\n6) **Image refinement workflow (practical, not theoretical)**\n- For top posts, produce visual brief + 2–3 prompt iterations each.\n- Select final image direction per post.\n- **Deliverable:** `IMAGE_BRIEFS_V1.md` + prompt set.\n\n7) **Final queue pack**\n- Sort by posting order/cadence.\n- Mark ready vs needs-review.\n- **Deliverable:** `POST_QUEUE_READY.md`.\n\n---\n\n## Tools/Skills to Add (today)\n\n### Must-add now\n- **Google Docs integration skill/tool** (read + critique drafts)\n- **Image generation/refinement workflow tool** (prompt versioning + selection rubric)\n- **Content memory tracker** (anti-repeat log for used hooks/themes)\n- **Ingestion updater** (new article → reindex pipeline command)\n\n### Nice-to-add (if time permits)\n- **Source citation validator** (checks every draft has evidence links)\n- **Queue formatter** (exports platform-ready copy blocks)\n\n---\n\n## EOD Success Criteria\n- Guardrails enforced\n- New-article update process defined\n- Idea bank complete\n- Queue-ready post batch created\n- Image directions ready for priority posts\n\nIf you want, I’ll start immediately with **Task 1 (skill research + setup)** and report back with a hard yes/no install list before touching anything risky.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba4eaab8fc819ba22c060ae4108e59\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":252,"output":786,"cacheRead":25472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26510,"cost":{"input":0.000441,"output":0.011004,"cacheRead":0.0044576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0159026}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773817507653}}
