{"type":"message","id":"8c790cb6","parentId":"03a3fca9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T07:13:48.685Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_rRLO4YoUZe0ztVU0u1vvAJoh|fc_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba50ac2c80819b915de3ec5761583f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Skills Research — 2026-03-17\n\n## Objective\nFind useful skills for Tiny's work (Nava content ops, LinkedIn + X execution) while avoiding risky installs.\n\n## Current baseline\nReady skills: healthcheck, session-logs, skill-creator, tmux, weather.\n\n## Candidate categories\n1. **Content ingestion/summarization**\n   - Candidate: `summarize` (bundled, missing local binary requirement)\n   - Value: Converts long-form source material into post-ready brief inputs.\n\n2. **X/Twitter execution**\n   - Candidate: `xurl` (bundled, requires xurl + auth)\n   - Value: Enables controlled publish/reply/search workflows for X.\n\n3. **Trend monitoring / RSS**\n   - Candidate: `blogwatcher` (bundled, requires blogwatcher binary)\n   - Value: Detects topic shifts and feeds content ideation pipeline.\n\n## ClawHub scan notes\nSearches run for: LinkedIn content, Twitter/X posting, RSS monitoring.\nTop results were mostly community skills with unknown trust posture.\n\n## Safety gate before install (proposed)\nOnly install if all pass:\n- Clear maintainer identity/history.\n- No hidden external-write behavior.\n- Minimal dependency footprint.\n- No shell execution patterns that bypass approval expectations.\n- Scope matches Tiny's workflow directly.\n\n## Auto-install decision tonight\nNo community skill auto-installed yet (conservative by design).\n\n## Next step (tomorrow briefing)\nBring a rank-ordered list:\n- Install now (low-risk, high-value)\n- Install with review\n- Avoid\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773818028658}}
