{"type":"message","id":"526383c9","parentId":"3ac38a8d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:31:17.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba62d0171c819b94d95e4469c0b68a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpumLRxyYACc9eVmF_ud9NRhlkYyI0r0oLCMUR10b_77uD8h3kLlmYdi0R3C4bfiL0ifj0xbi_X5p0tFCYgCtSic4F_8SeG05K-6Ug52SbUbcVhZTDENC9P4Wx-5QskBfBIXivpl1l5yWMHQe56JzmhvxE0qJJxxM7BZmHP04q6P-xMu7wND6If9oEKr2BUMLU5z7mDhzIeWDjttR8Y3HSrpZPIZRcSoocgV8qYYSxbUwWjMSCfrno7auaKlFdmmXDeRGHBI2daOzFYjng2wYkgXXmv-I9NSYxHz0sJ3T2yZMLlMjOS4CgiG7Vg12h5NibDZagOnAGojpWNq3nCZ1EaBh_x50CiVvJh9d5wQ-1YR55f4SXSXNA4CpzZdMOFNg0SPKh_hWxViIighFu9oK_OyQ_ICD043Hv297ZtZC3ST-lwBZFVxGexluVLWCq3JhXdNhAwtXOO1avdRJjst58KprzlRtoxjfGRd5PUDiYZVY2uE3AYsVTUY-LxwNF0UX4AiOf-7Kkg8Qh35kHJlsnNU1SbQqg6sh0Qk1KvWHY-7gw0VmN09pkV1qeEpWfQnF_nqbzGPv8d_hStHuL7NOWB4FRaiDONxDUg6OPzakfDXjYh02V0pygfS31Hfp9IH9AMcfDUOiOO5OQ4v22b3i-beNRGnefDKg96gfvuBExlFdy5HB0zv-UAbykIJ_IDMQ47NfrmkR8dl4JcIhIHjKSAqoKWnWNPyI0KBWBnmLH5lIyvMux_tebYVRArIpmaz8N37delpFU0VBeLi2MHXelrgeGqfNtm58lwb3NgDy_6fIcN6PLUHdcHGgXL2V2591pnUT3DB5Tc36CAtlr5qwkw4MFJtrSuC8Ya5HgcgEhqn1BpQ0arAU21X9qpAC5y-eIbkP1\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] PowerShell is fine — **it’s not a CMD vs PowerShell issue**.\n\nWhat’s likely happening:\n- connection interruptions or Ollama service hiccups,\n- and the progress display looks like “from scratch” even when blobs may still be cached.\n\nDo this to stabilize:\n\n1) Keep GUI closed  \n2) In PowerShell, restart Ollama service once:\n```powershell\nGet-Process ollama -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force\nStart-Process \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Programs\\Ollama\\ollama app.exe\"\n```\n3) Wait 10–15s, then retry pull:\n```powershell\nollama pull qwen3:4b-instruct\n```\n4) Don’t close terminal while downloading.\n\nIf it still loops, we’ll switch to a smaller model first to validate pipeline, then retry 4B.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba62d15590819b8426e2b01ed4edd6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":44126,"output":206,"cacheRead":2560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46892,"cost":{"input":0.0772205,"output":0.002884,"cacheRead":0.000448,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0805525}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773822659368}}
