{"type":"message","id":"a1d7a1ae","parentId":"43996c81","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:35:23.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Exactly — I mean the **browser/webchat interface** (this chat surface), not the TUI.\n\nFrom TUI alone, I can’t see your local screen unless you send image files into chat.  \nIf uploading is easier later, switch to browser and drop screenshots there.\n\nFor now in TUI, paste:\n- exact error text\n- model name/tag\n- and what the progress line does (e.g., resets at X%).","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba63c9fbfc819b99e4e2fe4952a08d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":388,"output":98,"cacheRead":46848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47334,"cost":{"input":0.000679,"output":0.001372,"cacheRead":0.0081984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010249399999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773822918730}}
