{"type":"message","id":"fd9c858a","parentId":"f64059d0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:17:21.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aLvZ74YcRBpPf1UEqG3SMNwR|fc_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba6d9abb28819b839eb4800fb909fc","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/OLLAMA_OPENAI_FALLBACK_GUIDE.md","oldText":"### Pattern B (preferred scripted switch)\nUse a tiny preflight script:\n1) check Ollama reachability\n2) if reachable -> set OpenClaw model to local alias\n3) else -> set OpenClaw model to OpenAI fallback\n\nExample (PowerShell):\n```powershell\ntry {\n  $r = Invoke-WebRequest -UseBasicParsing http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/tags -TimeoutSec 2\n  if ($r.StatusCode -eq 200) {\n    openclaw models set ollama/qwen3:4b-instruct\n  } else {\n    openclaw models set openai-codex/gpt-5.3-codex\n  }\n}\ncatch {\n  openclaw models set openai-codex/gpt-5.3-codex\n}\n```\n","newText":"### Pattern B (preferred scripted switch)\nUse the included preflight script:\n\n- Script path: `scripts/openclaw-model-preflight.ps1`\n- Behavior:\n  1) checks Ollama reachability\n  2) if reachable -> sets OpenClaw model to local alias\n  3) else -> sets OpenClaw model to OpenAI fallback\n\nRun it from PowerShell:\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\scripts\\openclaw-model-preflight.ps1\n```\n\nOptional custom args:\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\scripts\\openclaw-model-preflight.ps1 -OllamaModel \"ollama/qwen3:4b-instruct\" -FallbackModel \"openai-codex/gpt-5.3-codex\"\n```\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/OLLAMA_OPENAI_FALLBACK_GUIDE.md\",\"oldText\":\"### Pattern B (preferred scripted switch)\\nUse a tiny preflight script:\\n1) check Ollama reachability\\n2) if reachable -> set OpenClaw model to local alias\\n3) else -> set OpenClaw model to OpenAI fallback\\n\\nExample (PowerShell):\\n```powershell\\ntry {\\n  $r = Invoke-WebRequest -UseBasicParsing http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/tags -TimeoutSec 2\\n  if ($r.StatusCode -eq 200) {\\n    openclaw models set ollama/qwen3:4b-instruct\\n  } else {\\n    openclaw models set openai-codex/gpt-5.3-codex\\n  }\\n}\\ncatch {\\n  openclaw models set openai-codex/gpt-5.3-codex\\n}\\n```\\n\",\"newText\":\"### Pattern B (preferred scripted switch)\\nUse the included preflight script:\\n\\n- Script path: `scripts/openclaw-model-preflight.ps1`\\n- Behavior:\\n  1) checks Ollama reachability\\n  2) if reachable -> sets OpenClaw model to local alias\\n  3) else -> sets OpenClaw model to OpenAI fallback\\n\\nRun it from PowerShell:\\n```powershell\\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\\\scripts\\\\openclaw-model-preflight.ps1\\n```\\n\\nOptional custom args:\\n```powershell\\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\\\scripts\\\\openclaw-model-preflight.ps1 -OllamaModel \\\"ollama/qwen3:4b-instruct\\\" -FallbackModel \\\"openai-codex/gpt-5.3-codex\\\"\\n```\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":505,"output":426,"cacheRead":67072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68003,"cost":{"input":0.00088375,"output":0.005964,"cacheRead":0.011737599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01858535}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773825431394}}
