{"type":"message","id":"fe653ffe","parentId":"e94147f7","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:17:38.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done — I added the preflight script.\n\n### Where to find the guide\n- `OLLAMA_OPENAI_FALLBACK_GUIDE.md`  \n(full path: `/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/OLLAMA_OPENAI_FALLBACK_GUIDE.md`)\n\n### Script I added\n- `scripts/openclaw-model-preflight.ps1`  \n(full path: `/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/openclaw-model-preflight.ps1`)\n\nRun from workspace in PowerShell:\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\scripts\\openclaw-model-preflight.ps1\n```\n\n### About closing Qwen when idle\n- If idle and your system is fine, you *can* leave it running.\n- But best practice is: **close it when not actively using it** (frees RAM headroom and avoids surprise pressure spikes).\n\nSo: not mandatory, but I recommend closing unless you’re about to use it immediately.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169ba6daeb748819b8ae556652ee29d3c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":215,"output":218,"cacheRead":67968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68401,"cost":{"input":0.00037625,"output":0.003052,"cacheRead":0.0118944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01532265}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773825450412}}
