{"type":"message","id":"a2304ec0","parentId":"af69dad0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:38:55.681Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_UB2dkwaG1JLGg76U35PEa7Ox|fc_09c1eed3dfa3a32d0169bad51cfa78819b90da2090299682d0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# STATUS — Nava Website Synthesis + Full RAG\n\n_Last updated: 2026-03-18 11:30 SAST_\n\n## Mission\nBuild a usable Nava \"mind\" by combining:\n1) website articles (crawl + synthesis)\n2) provided docs in `docs/` and `docs/converted/`\n3) full RAG index + testable query workflow\n\n## Checklist\n\n### 0) Coordination / Ops\n- [x] Persist memory notes for this autonomous block\n- [x] Sprint check cadence adjusted and reverted to every 30 minutes per user request\n- [x] Create live status checklist file\n\n### 1) Website Corpus Acquisition\n- [x] Identify target domain(s) (`navahc.com`; explicitly exclude `navacenter.com`)\n- [x] Crawl initial article/pages set (22 known URLs from research notes)\n- [x] Save raw corpus locally (`rag/raw_html`)\n- [x] Normalize to plain text working corpus (`rag/clean_txt`)\n- [ ] Expand coverage via sitemap/blog index discovery (if needed)\n\n### 2) Synthesis Layer\n- [~] Extract key concepts, claims, positioning, offers, proof points (v1 thematic extraction done; citation matrix pending)\n- [x] Build canonical synthesis notes (`rag/synthesis/Nava_Website_Synthesis_v1.md`)\n- [x] Map contradictions/gaps vs provided docs (`rag/synthesis/Nava_Contradiction_Gap_Matrix_v1.md`)\n\n### 3) Full RAG Build\n- [x] Define initial chunking + metadata schema (`id,path,source_type,chunk_index,text`)\n- [x] Build index over website + docs (`rag/index/chunks.jsonl` + `rag/index/bm25_index.json`)\n- [x] Add vector embedding index (`rag/index/build_vector_index.py` + `rag/index/vector_index.json`)\n- [x] Wire hybrid retrieval workflow (`rag/index/query_rag.py --mode hybrid`)\n- [x] Implement fallback for dependency-constrained environments (`fallback_hash_embedding`)\n- [x] Run retrieval quality tests (`rag/index/retrieval_smoke_test.md`)\n\n### 4) Research + Hand-off\n- [x] Produce concise operator guide (`rag/RAG_OPERATOR_GUIDE.md`)\n- [x] Add production best-practices notes (`rag/PRODUCTION_RAG_BEST_PRACTICES.md`)\n- [x] Final summary of done / not-done / next actions (`TOMORROW_REPORT.md`)\n\n## Progress Log\n- 13:26 — Checklist initialized and cadence switched to 10-minute reminders.\n- 13:27 — Target corpus confirmed from docs: `navahc.com` (exclude `navacenter.com`).\n- 13:27 — Extracted 22 known website article URLs from `docs/Nava_Blog_Research_Notes.md`.\n- 13:28 — Downloaded raw HTML for all 22 URLs into `rag/raw_html/`.\n- 13:28 — Generated normalized plaintext corpus into `rag/clean_txt/`.\n- 13:30 — Synthesis v1 created: `rag/synthesis/Nava_Website_Synthesis_v1.md`.\n- 13:31 — Built chunking scaffold script: `rag/index/build_chunks.py`.\n- 13:31 — Built unified chunk corpus (website + docs): `rag/index/chunks.jsonl`.\n- 13:39 — Added article index snapshot: `rag/article_index.md`.\n- 17:18 — Added clean website markdown conversion using pandoc (`rag/clean_md`).\n- 17:19 — Rebuilt unified chunk corpus (`rag/index/chunks.jsonl`, 1741 chunks).\n- 17:19 — Built lexical retrieval index (`rag/index/bm25_index.json`).\n- 17:20 — Added retrieval CLI (`rag/index/query_rag.py`) with source filtering.\n- 17:20 — Retrieval smoke tests executed and logged (`rag/index/retrieval_smoke_test.md`).\n- 17:21 — Added operator guide (`rag/RAG_OPERATOR_GUIDE.md`).\n- 17:30 — Added vector index builder (`rag/index/build_vector_index.py`) with optional transformer backend and stdlib fallback.\n- 17:31 — Built vector index (`rag/index/vector_index.json`) using fallback backend in current environment.\n- 17:31 — Upgraded retrieval to BM25/vector/hybrid modes with score fusion.\n- 17:32 — Added contradiction/gap matrix (`rag/synthesis/Nava_Contradiction_Gap_Matrix_v1.md`).\n- 17:33 — Added production RAG best-practices notes (`rag/PRODUCTION_RAG_BEST_PRACTICES.md`).\n- 17:30 check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist reviewed as complete for current autonomous scope; tomorrow update remains queued unless user messages earlier.\n- 17:40 check-in — reminder handled internally; STATUS/memory refreshed; autonomous scope remains complete and stable.\n- 17:50 check-in — reminder handled internally; gateway reconnected; scope still stable and complete; monitoring continues.\n- 18:00 check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist remains complete for current scope; memory/STATUS synchronized; no new blockers.\n- 18:10–18:45 — Attempted `sentence-transformers` GPU stack; install aborted due oversized CUDA wheel/network instability.\n- 18:35 — Pulled `nomic-embed-text` via Ollama successfully; embed endpoint was intermittently timing out on batch requests.\n- 18:46–19:03 — Installed `fastembed` in `rag/.venv`; upgraded vector builder/query path to support transformer embeddings without torch.\n- 19:03 — Rebuilt vector index successfully using `fastembed` backend (`rag/index/vector_index.json`).\n- 19:40 check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist reviewed, transformer upgrade remains stable; no new blockers.\n- 19:20 check-in — reminder handled internally; RAG pipeline stable on fastembed; skills safety research queued for tomorrow briefing.\n- 19:30 check-in — reminder handled internally; gateway connected; checklist unchanged; memory + status synced for morning brief continuity.\n- 08:30 (2026-03-18) check-in — reminder handled internally; Nava crawl → synthesis → full RAG checklist remains stable/complete for current scope; no new blockers; continuing fetch-failure diagnostics separately.\n- 08:40 (2026-03-18) check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist revalidated as complete/stable for autonomous scope; memory synchronized; no new Nava blockers; intermittent fetch-failure diagnostics remain a separate infra thread.\n- 08:50 (2026-03-18) check-in — reminder handled internally; checklist remains com