l contradictions found; primary issue is **coverage gap** (docs contain stricter strategy/policy detail than website corpus).\\n- Hybrid retrieval is operational and returns relevant results across both corpora.\\n- Current environment used fallback vector backend (no transformer embeddings available at build time).\\n\\n## What to Do Next\\n1. Add metadata enrichment pass (`theme`, `audience`, `offer`, `evidence_level`, `risk_type`).\\n2. Build citation map extraction for claim-level grounding.\\n3. Create a 50-query eval set and track Recall@k/MRR/groundedness.\\n4. If runtime allows, install and benchmark transformer embeddings vs fallback backend.\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1773767379545}}\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/ce1da4a1-7a07-4db0-901c-0459b3dab2bf.jsonl.reset.2026-03-18T05-43-21.610Z:373:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"43a8de48\",\"parentId\":\"af29de27\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:09:46.448Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Updating documentation and preparing commit**\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0278252ab7917d830169b98ad6db348191a4f8fb2c844862eb\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABpuYrZ2RugiTPFAOmPiNW45EgUaAODuASCKiNIJuTFa_3NI6hlQmR9Luy_raUKiHucmBlTQAu3Q0ox0mhRppxlURGH0LJjLJRXi0NO9kle627uxm-KRa6SRV7rbMcNzUfLWjlxdsln6B2qU04C8wrl6p_YoDdenOKTq9UeoMqk1H2UNF6nbIu36b8H3kyVldNKrEqdlnYOKdVRYSL9CJKhKpSIVOC6efz_NqHTSfZTfy8Xs_G_v0bX8SxU3mUj9UMmJYmXI-ct8XLwbg8V09Ak8FYHv30w53f0vfKECPYOsD-lyjwPmvXPB9ytob1o_OrywCktEwDmhNIuQv5ODVQYdLbFOtfU44F_X2liCkOkLLY5tNTkI8GiQz8935USXOXiHI8-V_p7LubP7imqmvj0FLTyYIxo0t9-fj7tPb6-vX2fU-TQ60K-ZhqXovjmAOJ4WOOpBnus3BNPcdfIr9d8tnG9RrwpIR2Ri2izASe0P-qfNVwsqD5Rt9EnHit8N2ONex0a0WEy-4OvaINvWuDArK-dI9TYLullTPvzxpPG8OiN4KF8eiwCrnABYWfu0g7ie3VbhTwspeJ1mir8tZSzeQ6ioBVabbdynVzLjk-HoFU3NDGWmtCBo3ODRUsxHEvDA5fULZrpzOOyaYJoToV05o_hoLyE1XwBIk-O2557nf9sZmK_oKiRPeoVarefWoeX0gJjEt6wtl6WY_Prwx--PqliMYET5MXs3m_G6fxR