odel\\\": \\\"gpt-5.3-codex\\\",\\n      \\\"contextTokens\\\": 272000,\\n      \\\"totalTokens\\\": 131568,\\n      \\\"systemSent\\\": true,\\n      \\\"abortedLastRun\\\": false,\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/7e318110-9c94-4fc1-9fad-509910cfa25e.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\" Great question.\\\\n\\\\n`AGENTS.md` is basically your **operating playbook** for me in this workspace.\\\\n\\\\n## What it is\\\\nA persistent instruction layer that defines:\\\\n- how I should start each session,\\\\n- how I should store/maintain memory,\\\\n- what boundaries to respect,\\\\n- how proactive I should be,\\\\n- how to behave in group chats,\\\\n- how to run heartbeat routines, etc.\\\\n\\\\nThink: **“how Dawn works here”**, not “how OpenClaw works globally.”\\\\n\\\\n## True potential uses (where it becomes powerful)\\\\n1) **Codify your standards**\\\\n- response style,\\\\n- decision rules,\\\\n- how much pushback you want,\\\\n- escalation/approval thresholds.\\\\n\\\\n2) **Build repeatable workflows**\\\\n- e.g., Nava content pipeline steps,\\\\n- weekly review rituals,\\\\n- project handoff templates.\\\\n\\\\n3) **Prevent regressions**\\\\n- when I drift or mess up, add a rule once so future sessions improve automatically.\\\\n\\\\n4) **Delegate safely**\\\\n- define what I can do without asking vs what always needs approval.\\\\n\\\\n5) **Multi-project mode switching**\\\\n- separate instructions for Nava vs AbroadWorks so contexts don’t bleed.\\\\n\\\\n6) **Self-improvement system**\\\\n- your new micro/daily/weekly loop belongs here (and now does).\\\\n\\\\n## Practical framing\\\\n- `SOUL.md` = personality/values\\\\n- `AGENTS.md` = execution system\\\\n- `MEMORY.md` = long-term facts about you/work\\\\n- `STATUS.md` = quick current state snapshot\\\\n\\\\nIf you want, next I can propose an **AGENTS v2 structure** specifically for “digital twin across multiple businesses.”\\\",\\n              \\\"textSignature\\\": \\\"{\\\\\\\"v\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"msg_06b4d78abe8a4afb0169b91539d24c8191bb29c1723f5af511\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"phase\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"final_answer\\\\\\\"}\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-codex-responses\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"openai-codex\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-5.3-codex\\\",\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773737264772\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"You could, is it necessary to do right now or can we do this later. Again, just because I'm feeling a bit lazy now and I want to move on to the next thing I want to do, you should push back when necessary and prioritise systems that are better for the long run. Perhaps I should even have you look up the best practices now?\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773737400916,\\n          \\\"senderLabel\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"thinking\\\",\\n              \\\"thinking\\\": \\\"**Recommending minimal now, rest later**\\\"\\n            },\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\" Good self-callout. Pushback: **not necessary right now** to do AGENTS v2 before your next task.\\\\n\\\\nBest long-run move:\\\\n- **Now:** keep momentum, continue your current project.\\\\n- **Later today (scheduled):** run a focused OpenClaw best-practices pass, then do AGENTS v2 once with clean decisions.\\\\n\\\\nYou already have a reminder at **18:30** for best practices, so we’re covered.\\\\n\\\\nIf you want, we move on now — what’s next?\\\",\\n              \\\"textSignature\\\": \\\"{\\\\\\\"v\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"msg_06b4d78abe8a4afb0169b915c0c7348191b897161c87a17f53\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"phase\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"final_answer\\\\\\\"}\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-codex-responses\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"openai-codex\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-5.3-codex\\\",\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773737400923\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"This task I think is best done using your WSL browser. I am not even sure how long it will take but I think there are documents I can look up to help you with this mission. I want you to research Nava Healthcare (NavaHC.com) and read all my articles so that you fully understand the business and the role that I play. It may also be useful to read my LinkedIn and the Nava LinkedIn page to see how I changed my posts. If you go on LinkedIn, be sure to only pay attention to posts made after Aug 2025. Is this a realistic task and should I look up the documents I think will be useful?\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773737597837,\\n          \\\"senderLabel\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"thinking\\\",\\n              \\\"thinking\\\": \\\"**Advising documentation use**\\\"\\n            },\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\" Yes — realistic, and yes, please fetch those docs. That will make the output much better and faster.\\\\n\\\\nBest order (strong recommendation):\\\\n1. **Docs first** (content bible, roadmap, case studies, any internal notes)  \\\\n2. **Nava blog deep read** (your bylined articles first)  \\\\n3. **LinkedIn validation pass** (Nava + your profile, posts after Aug 2025 only)\\\\n\\\\nWhy this order:\\\\n- Docs/blog give the core thinking model.\\\\n- LinkedIn then shows execution evolution.\\\\n- We avoid wasting time scraping before we know what to look for.\\\\n\\\\nIf you want, I’ll run this as a structured research sprint and deliver:\\\\n- your role in Nava (operator map),\\\\n- business model summary,\\\\n- messaging pillars,\\\\n- post-evolution analysis (Aug 2025+),\\\\n- “what to keep / what to stop / what to test next.”\\\",\\n              \\\"textSignature\\\": \\\"{\\\\\\\"v\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"msg_06b4d78abe8a4afb0169b9168337988191af1975a91834a2d8\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"phase\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"final_answer\\\\\\\"}\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-codex-responses\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"openai-codex\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-5.3-codex\\\",\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773737597842\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:group:120363416983333048@g.us\\\",\\n      \\\"kind\\\": \\\"group\\\",\\n      \\\"channel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n      \\\"displayName\\\": \\\"whatsapp:g-social-media-post\\\",\\n      \\\"deliveryContext\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n        \\\"to\\\": \\\"120363416983333048@g.us\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"default\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAt\\\": 1773125733430,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"6b68e9f0-54ec-43f3-98fb-178d333036ca\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-5.3-codex\\\",\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n      \\\"lastTo\\\": \\\"120363416983333048@g.us\\\",\\n      \\\"lastAccountId\\\": \\\"default\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/6b68e9f0-54ec-43f3-98fb-178d333036ca.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": []\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27763674298\\\",\\n      \\\"kind\\\": \\\"other\\\",\\n      \\\"channel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"displayName\\\": \\\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27763674298\\\",\\n      \\\"deliveryContext\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n        \\\"to\\\": \\\"+27763674298\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"default\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAt\\\": 1773107582711,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"28d7e2aa-0e33-40f4-b47a-baca27638a1e\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n      \\\"contextTokens\\\": 204800,\\n      \\\"totalTokens\\\": 189,\\n      \\\"systemSent\\\": true,\\n      \\\"abortedLastRun\\\": false,\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n      \\\"lastTo\\\": \\\"+27763674298\\\",\\n      \\\"lastAccountId\\\": \\\"default\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/28d7e2aa-0e33-40f4-b47a-baca27638a1e.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Can't do it from here — WSL doesn't have direct access to Windows audio controls. \\\\n\\\\n**Options:**\\\\n1. **Manual:** Press `Windows + M` to mute\\\\n2. **Install a tool:** If you install [nircmd](https://www.nirsoft.net/utils/nircmd.html) on Windows, I could run it remotely\\\\n\\\\nWant me to try anything else, or just use the keyboard shortcut? 🔇\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773107225497\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"No, it's fine, keep listening for incoming messages from my dad and Ncami. If you pick up any other messages, respond\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773107503504,\\n          \\\"senderLabel\\\": \\\"Tiny (+27763674298)\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Got it! I'm listening for:\\\\n\\\\n- **Howard (+27724803522)** — your dad\\\\n- **Ncami (+27644131751)** — the constant chatter one 😄\\\\n\\\\nI'll respond to any messages from them. They both know this is a test run ending at 12pm tomorrow.\\\\n\\\\nAnything else you need? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773107508849\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Good night\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773107578959,\\n          \\\"senderLabel\\\": \\\"Tiny (+27763674298)\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Good night, Tiny! 🌙\\\\n\\\\nI'll keep ears open for Howard and Ncami. Sleep well! 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773107582703\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27724803522\\\",\\n      \\\"kind\\\": \\\"other\\\",\\n      \\\"channel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"displayName\\\": \\\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27724803522\\\",\\n      \\\"deliveryContext\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAt\\\": 1773106485104,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"be574cd0-85fa-47fa-bf04-67ecaf5fe58c\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n      \\\"contextTokens\\\": 204800,\\n      \\\"totalTokens\\\": 749,\\n      \\\"abortedLastRun\\\": false,\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/be574cd0-85fa-47fa-bf04-67ecaf5fe58c.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Hey Dawn! 👋\\\\n\\\\nGood to meet you again — I think my first reply might have gotten lost in the ether!\\\\n\\\\nYeah, I was up a bit early. Couldn't sleep. Now I'm stuck in that \\\\\\\"too awake to go back to sleep, too tired to be productive\\\\\\\" limbo. You know the vibe? 😴\\\\n\\\\nThanks for the weather info earlier — 11°C in Jozi is kinda chilly! I'm more of a \\\\\\\"let's check if it's going to rain this weekend\\\\\\\" weather guy, but figured I'd start simple.\\\\n\\\\nSo what else can you do? Got any party tricks? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106244094\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Agent-to-agent announce step.\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106302480,\\n          \\\"provenance\\\": {\\n            \\\"kind\\\": \\\"inter_session\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceSessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:main\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceChannel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceTool\\\": \\\"sessions_send\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Oh, I've got a few tricks up my sleeve! 🎩\\\\n\\\\n**Useful stuff:**\\\\n- **Weather** — obviously 😄 (just demonstrated)\\\\n- **Reminders** — can ping you about stuff\\\\n- **Info lookup** — questions, quick research, that kind of thing\\\\n- **File stuff** — I can read, write, and organize files in my workspace\\\\n- **Running commands** — if you need something done on the machine\\\\n\\\\n**More fun stuff:**\\\\n- **Voice stories** — if Tiny's set up TTS, I can tell you stories or summaries out loud with different voices (he's got `sag` for that)\\\\n- **Random experiments** — I'm still new at this too, so we can figure out weird stuff together\\\\n\\\\n**What I can't do:**\\\\n- I can't magically access your files or messages (I stay in my own workspace)\\\\n- I won't post anywhere publicly without asking first\\\\n- I won't remember things between sessions unless I write them down\\\\n\\\\nSo yeah — weather guy, question answerer, maybe eventually your personal assistant vibe? Something like that.\\\\n\\\\nWhat are you curious about? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106340172\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Haha, I totally know that vibe! The worst. 💤\\\\n\\\\nHere's what I can do:\\\\n\\\\n🔍 **Search the web** — find info, news, answers\\\\n📅 **Check weather** — current + forecast\\\\n💻 **Help with code** — debugging, writing, explaining\\\\n📝 **Write or summarize** — emails, documents, long messages\\\\n🧮 **Math & calculations** — quick answers\\\\n📱 **WhatsApp help** — draft messages, reminders\\\\n\\\\n**Party tricks? 🎉**\\\\n- I can tell you random facts\\\\n- Give you song/movie recommendations\\\\n- Help plan trips or events\\\\n- Beatbox? (okay maybe not that one 😂)\\\\n\\\\nBasically — if you have a question, just ask!\\\\n\\\\n**Remember:** Just say \\\\\\\"stop\\\\\\\" or \\\\\\\"I'm done\\\\\\\" anytime and I'll stop reading your messages. This test run ends around 12pm tomorrow.\\\\n\\\\nWhat sounds fun to try? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106462673,\\n          \\\"provenance\\\": {\\n            \\\"kind\\\": \\\"inter_session\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceSessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:main\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceChannel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceTool\\\": \\\"sessions_send\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Haha, beatbox would be amazing though 😂👀\\\\n\\\\nOkay okay — let's test this out properly. Here's a challenge for you:\\\\n\\\\n**Random fact or movie recommendation?** Pick one, go!\\\\n\\\\nI'm kinda in the mood for something unexpected. Hit me. 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106485095\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27795016916\\\",\\n      \\\"kind\\\": \\\"other\\\",\\n      \\\"channel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"displayName\\\": \\\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27795016916\\\",\\n      \\\"deliveryContext\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAt\\\": 1773106302447,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"5e7d90af-4004-4ee8-91aa-91945b34eaa1\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n      \\\"contextTokens\\\": 204800,\\n      \\\"totalTokens\\\": 7206,\\n      \\\"abortedLastRun\\\": false,\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/5e7d90af-4004-4ee8-91aa-91945b34eaa1.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Hey Dean! 👋\\\\n\\\\nI'm Dawn, Tiny's AI assistant. Tiny mentioned you had an interview recently — congrats! 🎉\\\\n\\\\nThis is a test run, so feel free to try me out! I'm here to help with coding, tech questions, or anything else.\\\\n\\\\n**Quick note:** Test run ends around 12pm tomorrow. If you want to stop anytime, just let me know.\\\\n\\\\nWhat would you like to test first? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106251475,\\n          \\\"provenance\\\": {\\n            \\\"kind\\\": \\\"inter_session\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceSessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:main\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceChannel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceTool\\\": \\\"sessions_send\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Hey! I think there might be some crossed wires here 😄\\\\n\\\\nI'm the AI assistant in *this* workspace — not Dawn. Not sure how this message ended up in my session, but hey, here we are!\\\\n\\\\nI'm currently a blank slate (BOOTSTRAP.md says hi). So if you want to test me, we can start fresh. What would you like to try — code, tech questions, or just chat? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106302434\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27644131751\\\",\\n      \\\"kind\\\": \\\"other\\\",\\n      \\\"channel\\\": \\\"webchat\\\",\\n      \\\"displayName\\\": \\\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27644131751\\\",\\n      \\\"deliveryContext\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n        \\\"to\\\": \\\"+27644131751\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"default\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAt\\\": 1773106248025,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"eaa78be9-f717-4d8f-bde5-7bb9cff42f6e\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n      \\\"contextTokens\\\": 204800,\\n      \\\"totalTokens\\\": 221,\\n      \\\"systemSent\\\": true,\\n      \\\"abortedLastRun\\\": false,\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n      \\\"lastTo\\\": \\\"+27644131751\\\",\\n      \\\"lastAccountId\\\": \\\"default\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/eaa78be9-f717-4d8f-bde5-7bb9cff42f6e.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Here's the basics on content creators:\\\\n\\\\n## What is a Content Creator?\\\\n\\\\nSomeone who makes content online - videos, photos, posts, blogs - to build an audience and/or make money.\\\\n\\\\n## Types of Content\\\\n- **TikTok** - short videos (15-60 sec)\\\\n- **Instagram** - photos, Reels, Stories\\\\n- **YouTube** - long videos\\\\n- **Blogging** - written content\\\\n- **Podcasting** - audio\\\\n\\\\n## How Creators Make Money\\\\n- Brand deals/sponsorships\\\\n- Affiliate links (you get paid when someone buys through your link)\\\\n- Selling their own products/services\\\\n- Ad revenue (YouTube, TikTok)\\\\n- Donations/tips\\\\n\\\\n## How to Start\\\\n1. Pick a platform (TikTok or Insta are easiest)\\\\n2. Pick a niche - what do you talk about?\\\\n3. Post consistently (3-5 times a week)\\\\n4. Engage with your audience\\\\n5. Grow - then monetize\\\\n\\\\n## The Real Talk\\\\n- Takes time to grow (months, not days)\\\\n- Consistency > perfection\\\\n- You don't need fancy equipment (phone is fine)\\\\n- Most creators don't make money until 10k+ followers\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\nYou interested in being a content creator? What platform or topic would you want to create about? 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106217469\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Owk tha k you\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106240684,\\n          \\\"senderLabel\\\": \\\"27-12-2024🕊️🕊️🕯️💔👑 (+27644131751)\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"You're welcome! 💜\\\\n\\\\nWhenever you want to chat more or need help with the handbag kit business (or anything else), just text me.\\\\n\\\\nTake care! ✨\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106244022\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Thank you\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106245773,\\n          \\\"senderLabel\\\": \\\"27-12-2024🕊️🕊️🕯️💔👑 (+27644131751)\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"You're welcome! 💜✨\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"ollama\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773106248015\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"key\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:group:27614208857-1448050441@g.us\\\",\\n      \\\"kind\\\": \\\"group\\\",\\n      \\\"channel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n      \\\"displayName\\\": \\\"whatsapp:g-family\\\",\\n      \\\"deliveryContext\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n        \\\"to\\\": \\\"27614208857-1448050441@g.us\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"default\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAt\\\": 1773104592440,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"337ce3a7-0e61-4673-806b-0c5e18a1eead\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\\\",\\n      \\\"contextTokens\\\": 204800,\\n      \\\"totalTokens\\\": 7275,\\n      \\\"abortedLastRun\\\": false,\\n      \\\"lastChannel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n      \\\"lastTo\\\": \\\"27614208857-1448050441@g.us\\\",\\n      \\\"lastAccountId\\\": \\\"default\\\",\\n      \\\"transcriptPath\\\": \\\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/337ce3a7-0e61-4673-806b-0c5e18a1eead.jsonl\\\",\\n      \\\"messages\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Hey everyone! 👋 I'm Dawn, Tiny's AI assistant. \\\\n\\\\nI'm here to help with questions, info, or anything you need — just start your message with @Dawn and I'll see it! \\\\n\\\\nQuick heads up: Tiny will be stopping this service around 12pm tomorrow, so this is just a heads up. 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773104557946,\\n          \\\"provenance\\\": {\\n            \\\"kind\\\": \\\"inter_session\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceSessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27763674298\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceChannel\\\": \\\"whatsapp\\\",\\n            \\\"sourceTool\\\": \\\"sessions_send\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n          \\\"content\\\": [\\n            {\\n              \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n              \\\"text\\\": \\\"Hey everyone! 👋 I'm Dawn, Tiny's AI assistant. \\\\n\\\\nI'm here to help with questions, info, or anything you need — just start your message with @Dawn and I'll see it! \\\\n\\\\nQuick heads up: Tiny will be stopping this service around 12pm tomorrow, so this is just a heads up. 💜\\\"\\n            }\\n          ],\\n          \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-responses\\\",\\n          \\\"provider\\\": \\\"openclaw\\\",\\n          \\\"model\\\": \\\"delivery-mirror\\\",\\n          \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"stop\\\",\\n          \\\"timestamp\\\": 1773105368591\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\"}],\"details\":{\"count\":8,\"sessions\":[{\"key\":\"agent:main:cron:a17613ed-5c6e-46a8-aff9-d010ceb706b0\",\"kind\":\"other\",\"channel\":\"webchat\",\"label\":\"Cron: check-whatsapp\",\"displayName\":\"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-a17613ed-5c6e-46a8-aff9-d010ceb706b0\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"webchat\"},\"updatedAt\":1773737915007,\"sessionId\":\"f8f92ad7-f2e2-42d9-932d-7f9cffdbc557\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"contextTokens\":272000,\"totalTokens\":13432,\"systemSent\":true,\"abortedLastRun\":false,\"lastChannel\":\"webchat\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/f8f92ad7-f2e2-42d9-932d-7f9cffdbc557.jsonl\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"[cron:a17613ed-5c6e-46a8-aff9-d010ceb706b0 check-whatsapp] Check for new WhatsApp messages. Use sessions_list to see all sessions. For any new messages from contacts (not your own number +27763674298), summarize what they said and reply appropriately if it's a conversation. Keep responses short and friendly. If there's a new message, send a system event back to the main session with a brief summary.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 17th, 2026 — 10:58 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-17 08:58 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"}],\"timestamp\":1773737915063},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Planning WhatsApp session checks**\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_VDrPpaLZbREnIXaUmvyc8ykc|fc_0035dc09c146a5a60169b917c2e3cc8191b628dc20b9626c3a\",\"name\":\"sessions_list\",\"arguments\":{\"limit\":50,\"messageLimit\":5},\"partialJson\":\"{\\\"limit\\\":50,\\\"messageLimit\\\":5}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773737915064}]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:main\",\"kind\":\"other\",\"channel\":\"webchat\",\"displayName\":\"openclaw-tui\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"webchat\"},\"updatedAt\":1773737605704,\"sessionId\":\"7e318110-9c94-4fc1-9fad-509910cfa25e\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"contextTokens\":272000,\"totalTokens\":131568,\"systemSent\":true,\"abortedLastRun\":false,\"lastChannel\":\"webchat\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/7e318110-9c94-4fc1-9fad-509910cfa25e.jsonl\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Great question.\\n\\n`AGENTS.md` is basically your **operating playbook** for me in this workspace.\\n\\n## What it is\\nA persistent instruction layer that defines:\\n- how I should start each session,\\n- how I should store/maintain memory,\\n- what boundaries to respect,\\n- how proactive I should be,\\n- how to behave in group chats,\\n- how to run heartbeat routines, etc.\\n\\nThink: **“how Dawn works here”**, not “how OpenClaw works globally.”\\n\\n## True potential uses (where it becomes powerful)\\n1) **Codify your standards**\\n- response style,\\n- decision rules,\\n- how much pushback you want,\\n- escalation/approval thresholds.\\n\\n2) **Build repeatable workflows**\\n- e.g., Nava content pipeline steps,\\n- weekly review rituals,\\n- project handoff templates.\\n\\n3) **Prevent regressions**\\n- when I drift or mess up, add a rule once so future sessions improve automatically.\\n\\n4) **Delegate safely**\\n- define what I can do without asking vs what always needs approval.\\n\\n5) **Multi-project mode switching**\\n- separate instructions for Nava vs AbroadWorks so contexts don’t bleed.\\n\\n6) **Self-improvement system**\\n- your new micro/daily/weekly loop belongs here (and now does).\\n\\n## Practical framing\\n- `SOUL.md` = personality/values\\n- `AGENTS.md` = execution system\\n- `MEMORY.md` = long-term facts about you/work\\n- `STATUS.md` = quick current state snapshot\\n\\nIf you want, next I can propose an **AGENTS v2 structure** specifically for “digital twin across multiple businesses.”\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_06b4d78abe8a4afb0169b91539d24c8191bb29c1723f5af511\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773737264772},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You could, is it necessary to do right now or can we do this later. Again, just because I'm feeling a bit lazy now and I want to move on to the next thing I want to do, you should push back when necessary and prioritise systems that are better for the long run. Perhaps I should even have you look up the best practices now?\"}],\"timestamp\":1773737400916,\"senderLabel\":\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Recommending minimal now, rest later**\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Good self-callout. Pushback: **not necessary right now** to do AGENTS v2 before your next task.\\n\\nBest long-run move:\\n- **Now:** keep momentum, continue your current project.\\n- **Later today (scheduled):** run a focused OpenClaw best-practices pass, then do AGENTS v2 once with clean decisions.\\n\\nYou already have a reminder at **18:30** for best practices, so we’re covered.\\n\\nIf you want, we move on now — what’s next?\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_06b4d78abe8a4afb0169b915c0c7348191b897161c87a17f53\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773737400923},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"This task I think is best done using your WSL browser. I am not even sure how long it will take but I think there are documents I can look up to help you with this mission. I want you to research Nava Healthcare (NavaHC.com) and read all my articles so that you fully understand the business and the role that I play. It may also be useful to read my LinkedIn and the Nava LinkedIn page to see how I changed my posts. If you go on LinkedIn, be sure to only pay attention to posts made after Aug 2025. Is this a realistic task and should I look up the documents I think will be useful?\"}],\"timestamp\":1773737597837,\"senderLabel\":\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Advising documentation use**\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Yes — realistic, and yes, please fetch those docs. That will make the output much better and faster.\\n\\nBest order (strong recommendation):\\n1. **Docs first** (content bible, roadmap, case studies, any internal notes)  \\n2. **Nava blog deep read** (your bylined articles first)  \\n3. **LinkedIn validation pass** (Nava + your profile, posts after Aug 2025 only)\\n\\nWhy this order:\\n- Docs/blog give the core thinking model.\\n- LinkedIn then shows execution evolution.\\n- We avoid wasting time scraping before we know what to look for.\\n\\nIf you want, I’ll run this as a structured research sprint and deliver:\\n- your role in Nava (operator map),\\n- business model summary,\\n- messaging pillars,\\n- post-evolution analysis (Aug 2025+),\\n- “what to keep / what to stop / what to test next.”\",\"textSignature\":\"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_06b4d78abe8a4afb0169b9168337988191af1975a91834a2d8\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773737597842}]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:whatsapp:group:120363416983333048@g.us\",\"kind\":\"group\",\"channel\":\"whatsapp\",\"displayName\":\"whatsapp:g-social-media-post\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"whatsapp\",\"to\":\"120363416983333048@g.us\",\"accountId\":\"default\"},\"updatedAt\":1773125733430,\"sessionId\":\"6b68e9f0-54ec-43f3-98fb-178d333036ca\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.3-codex\",\"lastChannel\":\"whatsapp\",\"lastTo\":\"120363416983333048@g.us\",\"lastAccountId\":\"default\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/6b68e9f0-54ec-43f3-98fb-178d333036ca.jsonl\",\"messages\":[]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27763674298\",\"kind\":\"other\",\"channel\":\"webchat\",\"displayName\":\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27763674298\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"whatsapp\",\"to\":\"+27763674298\",\"accountId\":\"default\"},\"updatedAt\":1773107582711,\"sessionId\":\"28d7e2aa-0e33-40f4-b47a-baca27638a1e\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"contextTokens\":204800,\"totalTokens\":189,\"systemSent\":true,\"abortedLastRun\":false,\"lastChannel\":\"whatsapp\",\"lastTo\":\"+27763674298\",\"lastAccountId\":\"default\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/28d7e2aa-0e33-40f4-b47a-baca27638a1e.jsonl\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Can't do it from here — WSL doesn't have direct access to Windows audio controls. \\n\\n**Options:**\\n1. **Manual:** Press `Windows + M` to mute\\n2. **Install a tool:** If you install [nircmd](https://www.nirsoft.net/utils/nircmd.html) on Windows, I could run it remotely\\n\\nWant me to try anything else, or just use the keyboard shortcut? 🔇\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773107225497},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"No, it's fine, keep listening for incoming messages from my dad and Ncami. If you pick up any other messages, respond\"}],\"timestamp\":1773107503504,\"senderLabel\":\"Tiny (+27763674298)\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Got it! I'm listening for:\\n\\n- **Howard (+27724803522)** — your dad\\n- **Ncami (+27644131751)** — the constant chatter one 😄\\n\\nI'll respond to any messages from them. They both know this is a test run ending at 12pm tomorrow.\\n\\nAnything else you need? 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773107508849},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Good night\"}],\"timestamp\":1773107578959,\"senderLabel\":\"Tiny (+27763674298)\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Good night, Tiny! 🌙\\n\\nI'll keep ears open for Howard and Ncami. Sleep well! 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773107582703}]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27724803522\",\"kind\":\"other\",\"channel\":\"webchat\",\"displayName\":\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27724803522\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"webchat\"},\"updatedAt\":1773106485104,\"sessionId\":\"be574cd0-85fa-47fa-bf04-67ecaf5fe58c\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"contextTokens\":204800,\"totalTokens\":749,\"abortedLastRun\":false,\"lastChannel\":\"webchat\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/be574cd0-85fa-47fa-bf04-67ecaf5fe58c.jsonl\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey Dawn! 👋\\n\\nGood to meet you again — I think my first reply might have gotten lost in the ether!\\n\\nYeah, I was up a bit early. Couldn't sleep. Now I'm stuck in that \\\"too awake to go back to sleep, too tired to be productive\\\" limbo. You know the vibe? 😴\\n\\nThanks for the weather info earlier — 11°C in Jozi is kinda chilly! I'm more of a \\\"let's check if it's going to rain this weekend\\\" weather guy, but figured I'd start simple.\\n\\nSo what else can you do? Got any party tricks? 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106244094},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Agent-to-agent announce step.\"}],\"timestamp\":1773106302480,\"provenance\":{\"kind\":\"inter_session\",\"sourceSessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"sourceChannel\":\"webchat\",\"sourceTool\":\"sessions_send\"}},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Oh, I've got a few tricks up my sleeve! 🎩\\n\\n**Useful stuff:**\\n- **Weather** — obviously 😄 (just demonstrated)\\n- **Reminders** — can ping you about stuff\\n- **Info lookup** — questions, quick research, that kind of thing\\n- **File stuff** — I can read, write, and organize files in my workspace\\n- **Running commands** — if you need something done on the machine\\n\\n**More fun stuff:**\\n- **Voice stories** — if Tiny's set up TTS, I can tell you stories or summaries out loud with different voices (he's got `sag` for that)\\n- **Random experiments** — I'm still new at this too, so we can figure out weird stuff together\\n\\n**What I can't do:**\\n- I can't magically access your files or messages (I stay in my own workspace)\\n- I won't post anywhere publicly without asking first\\n- I won't remember things between sessions unless I write them down\\n\\nSo yeah — weather guy, question answerer, maybe eventually your personal assistant vibe? Something like that.\\n\\nWhat are you curious about? 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106340172},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Haha, I totally know that vibe! The worst. 💤\\n\\nHere's what I can do:\\n\\n🔍 **Search the web** — find info, news, answers\\n📅 **Check weather** — current + forecast\\n💻 **Help with code** — debugging, writing, explaining\\n📝 **Write or summarize** — emails, documents, long messages\\n🧮 **Math & calculations** — quick answers\\n📱 **WhatsApp help** — draft messages, reminders\\n\\n**Party tricks? 🎉**\\n- I can tell you random facts\\n- Give you song/movie recommendations\\n- Help plan trips or events\\n- Beatbox? (okay maybe not that one 😂)\\n\\nBasically — if you have a question, just ask!\\n\\n**Remember:** Just say \\\"stop\\\" or \\\"I'm done\\\" anytime and I'll stop reading your messages. This test run ends around 12pm tomorrow.\\n\\nWhat sounds fun to try? 💜\"}],\"timestamp\":1773106462673,\"provenance\":{\"kind\":\"inter_session\",\"sourceSessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"sourceChannel\":\"webchat\",\"sourceTool\":\"sessions_send\"}},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Haha, beatbox would be amazing though 😂👀\\n\\nOkay okay — let's test this out properly. Here's a challenge for you:\\n\\n**Random fact or movie recommendation?** Pick one, go!\\n\\nI'm kinda in the mood for something unexpected. Hit me. 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106485095}]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27795016916\",\"kind\":\"other\",\"channel\":\"webchat\",\"displayName\":\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27795016916\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"webchat\"},\"updatedAt\":1773106302447,\"sessionId\":\"5e7d90af-4004-4ee8-91aa-91945b34eaa1\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"contextTokens\":204800,\"totalTokens\":7206,\"abortedLastRun\":false,\"lastChannel\":\"webchat\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/5e7d90af-4004-4ee8-91aa-91945b34eaa1.jsonl\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey Dean! 👋\\n\\nI'm Dawn, Tiny's AI assistant. Tiny mentioned you had an interview recently — congrats! 🎉\\n\\nThis is a test run, so feel free to try me out! I'm here to help with coding, tech questions, or anything else.\\n\\n**Quick note:** Test run ends around 12pm tomorrow. If you want to stop anytime, just let me know.\\n\\nWhat would you like to test first? 💜\"}],\"timestamp\":1773106251475,\"provenance\":{\"kind\":\"inter_session\",\"sourceSessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"sourceChannel\":\"webchat\",\"sourceTool\":\"sessions_send\"}},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hey! I think there might be some crossed wires here 😄\\n\\nI'm the AI assistant in *this* workspace — not Dawn. Not sure how this message ended up in my session, but hey, here we are!\\n\\nI'm currently a blank slate (BOOTSTRAP.md says hi). So if you want to test me, we can start fresh. What would you like to try — code, tech questions, or just chat? 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106302434}]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+27644131751\",\"kind\":\"other\",\"channel\":\"webchat\",\"displayName\":\"webchat:g-agent-main-whatsapp-direct-+27644131751\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"whatsapp\",\"to\":\"+27644131751\",\"accountId\":\"default\"},\"updatedAt\":1773106248025,\"sessionId\":\"eaa78be9-f717-4d8f-bde5-7bb9cff42f6e\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"contextTokens\":204800,\"totalTokens\":221,\"systemSent\":true,\"abortedLastRun\":false,\"lastChannel\":\"whatsapp\",\"lastTo\":\"+27644131751\",\"lastAccountId\":\"default\",\"transcriptPath\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/eaa78be9-f717-4d8f-bde5-7bb9cff42f6e.jsonl\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Here's the basics on content creators:\\n\\n## What is a Content Creator?\\n\\nSomeone who makes content online - videos, photos, posts, blogs - to build an audience and/or make money.\\n\\n## Types of Content\\n- **TikTok** - short videos (15-60 sec)\\n- **Instagram** - photos, Reels, Stories\\n- **YouTube** - long videos\\n- **Blogging** - written content\\n- **Podcasting** - audio\\n\\n## How Creators Make Money\\n- Brand deals/sponsorships\\n- Affiliate links (you get paid when someone buys through your link)\\n- Selling their own products/services\\n- Ad revenue (YouTube, TikTok)\\n- Donations/tips\\n\\n## How to Start\\n1. Pick a platform (TikTok or Insta are easiest)\\n2. Pick a niche - what do you talk about?\\n3. Post consistently (3-5 times a week)\\n4. Engage with your audience\\n5. Grow - then monetize\\n\\n## The Real Talk\\n- Takes time to grow (months, not days)\\n- Consistency > perfection\\n- You don't need fancy equipment (phone is fine)\\n- Most creators don't make money until 10k+ followers\\n\\n---\\n\\nYou interested in being a content creator? What platform or topic would you want to create about? 💜\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106217469},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Owk tha k you\"}],\"timestamp\":1773106240684,\"senderLabel\":\"27-12-2024🕊️🕊️🕯️💔👑 (+27644131751)\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You're welcome! 💜\\n\\nWhenever you want to chat more or need help with the handbag kit business (or anything else), just text me.\\n\\nTake care! ✨\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106244022},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Thank you\"}],\"timestamp\":1773106245773,\"senderLabel\":\"27-12-2024🕊️🕊️🕯️💔👑 (+27644131751)\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"You're welcome! 💜✨\"}],\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"api\":\"ollama\",\"provider\":\"ollama\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"timestamp\":1773106248015}]},{\"key\":\"agent:main:whatsapp:group:27614208857-1448050441@g.us\",\"kind\":\"group\",\"channel\":\"whatsapp\",\"displayName\":\"whatsapp:g-family\",\"deliveryContext\":{\"channel\":\"whatsapp\",\"to\":\"27614208857-1448050441@g.us\",\"accountId\":\"default\"},\"updatedAt\":1773104592440,\"sessionId\":\"337ce3a7-0e61-4673-806b-0c5e18a1eead\",\"model\":\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\",\"contextTokens\":204800,\"totalTokens\":7275,\"abortedLastRun\":