l optimization with manual switching (Llama lighter-model trial) and strict no-unapproved-config-mutations policy.\n- 17:30 (2026-03-18) check-in — reminder handled internally; Nava crawl → synthesis → full RAG status remains complete/stable with no new delivery blockers. User-directed model experimentation continues (moved from Qwen stress to lighter local options, currently testing Llama path) while preserving no-silent-config-change rule.\n- 18:00 (2026-03-18) check-in — reminder handled internally; Nava crawl → synthesis → full RAG scope remains complete/stable with no new content blockers. Local-model thread updated: `llama3.2:3b` rewrite test succeeded; initial JSON run was interrupted by PowerShell multiline parsing, then rerun produced valid JSON but schema drift (extra/altered fields), indicating partial reliability and need for stricter prompt contract before routing default changes.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773853286055}}
