{"type":"message","id":"c7283a1a","parentId":"66162e34","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:53:28.953Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**nemotron-3-super** is available in Ollama, but there's a catch:\n\n- **Size: ~230GB** — that's huge for a laptop. You'd need massive storage and RAM.\n\nThere's also a smaller option:\n- **nemotron-3-nano:30b** (~32GB) — more realistic\n\n### To pull it:\n\n```bash\nollama pull nemotron-3-super\n```\n\nOr if you mean **Ollama Cloud** (remote execution, not local):\n\n```bash\nollama run nemotron-3-super\n```\n\nThat would run on Nvidia's servers via Ollama's cloud integration.\n\n**How are you planning to run it?** Local (230GB download, huge RAM needs) or via Ollama Cloud?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":45219,"output":379,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773856408951}}
