{"type":"message","id":"2708b9f5","parentId":"b67a5c1e","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:55:29.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_5abf1f37-d07e-4314-a31b-f23a69e52a9f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"llama3.2:3b\"\n\"qwen3:4b-instruct\"\n\"nomic-embed-text:latest\"\n\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\"\n\"kimi-k2.5:cloud\"\n\"glm-5:cloud\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":21,"aggregated":"\"llama3.2:3b\"\n\"qwen3:4b-instruct\"\n\"nomic-embed-text:latest\"\n\"minimax-m2.5:cloud\"\n\"kimi-k2.5:cloud\"\n\"glm-5:cloud\"","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773856529816}}
{"type":"message","id":"3212c9bd","parentId":"2708b9f5","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:55:37.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your local Ollama has:\n- llama3.2:3b\n- qwen3:4b-instruct  \n- minimax-m2.5:cloud ← this already uses cloud\n- kimi-k2.5:cloud\n- glm-5:cloud\n\nSo models ending in `:cloud` are already running via Ollama's cloud service.\n\n**nemotron-3-super** isn't in your local list — you'd need to either:\n\n1. **Pull it** → Downloads 230GB locally (too big for laptop)\n2. **Use Ollama Cloud directly** → Requires their API\n\nTo check if you have Ollama Cloud access, try:\n\n```bash\nollama run nemotron-3-super \"Hi\"\n```\n\nThat should prompt you to log in or use cloud if available.\n\n**Alternative:** Your existing cloud models (`minimax-m2.5:cloud`, `kimi-k2.5:cloud`) are already using remote GPUs. Any of those work as your brain?\n\nWant me to test one of those instead?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":46575,"output":518,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47093,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773856537570}}
