{"type":"message","id":"53e7f393","parentId":"84db6d2e","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:58:48.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nice! Here's how to connect me to Ollama Cloud:\n\n**Step 1: Set the API key**\n\nIn WSL, run:\n\n```bash\nexport OLLAMA_API_KEY=\"your-api-key-here\"\n```\n\nOr to make it permanent, add to your `~/.bashrc`:\n\n```bash\necho 'export OLLAMA_API_KEY=\"your-api-key-here\"' >> ~/.bashrc\nsource ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n**Step 2: Test the connection**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d '{\"model\": \"nemotron-3-super\", \"prompt\": \"Hi\", \"stream\": false}' -H \"Authorization: Bearer $OLLAMA_API_KEY\"\n```\n\n**Step 3: Switch me to it**\n\nOnce it's working:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw models set ollama/nemotron-3-super\nopenclaw models status --plain\n```\n\nGo ahead and set the API key, then tell me when you're ready and I'll test it!"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":46891,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47188,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773856728211}}
